6.2 维护堆的性质
维护堆伪代码实现：
heap = [27,17,3,16,13,10,1,5,7,12,4,8,9,0]
i = 2

def MaxHeapify(heap,i):
    heapLenth = len(heap)
    l = 2*i+1
    r = 2*i+2
    largest = i
    if l <= heapLenth-1 and heap[l] > heap[i]:
        largest = l
    if r <= heapLenth-1 and heap[r] > heap[largest]:
        largest = r
    if largest != i:
        heap[i],heap[largest]=heap[largest],heap[i]
        MaxHeapify(heap,largest)

MaxHeapify(heap,i)
print (heap)
练习：
